  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1999910/extras/71dc3697018dfab8d6bd80064e87f60a.webp?t=1744102966\" width=300 height=20 /></span><br><strong><i>Start to the hunting Nightmare</i></strong><br><br><strong><i>Story about background</i></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1999910/extras/00eea8d99e4c92344e8cd436ea663876.avif?t=1744102966\" width=200 height=100 /></span><br>Nightmares keep invading.<br>The only way to stop them is to hold on until dawn!!<br><br><strong>Feature</strong><br><i>3 types of enemies</i><br>Chaser: They look like eyeballs, but if you touch them, they will chew you up.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1999910/extras/e4732c3c0d937e781a8e04d30a3ae811.poster.avif?t=1744102966\" width=512 height=512 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1999910/extras/e4732c3c0d937e781a8e04d30a3ae811.webm?t=1744102966\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Witness: They seem to be in place, but they come closer to you little by little.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1999910/extras/c2de7558fc07f3390f3262c6c20af5bf.apng?t=1744102966\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1999910/extras/c2de7558fc07f3390f3262c6c20af5bf.poster.avif?t=1744102966\" class=\"bb_img\" width=256 height=256 /></picture></span><br><br>Blind: For some reason, they're sealed, but they fire stingers in response to your gunfire.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1999910/extras/9fe9e191be8106f50bc6bebae4dc36d3.apng?t=1744102966\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1999910/extras/9fe9e191be8106f50bc6bebae4dc36d3.poster.avif?t=1744102966\" class=\"bb_img\" width=256 height=256 /></picture></span><br><br><strong><i>4 types of items</i></strong><br>Basic Guns: Only basic weapons have no time limit.<br>2 shots: You can get it randomly by killing the Chaser.<br>3 shots: The most useful weapon. It can be obtained randomly by defeating the Chaser.<br>Red Shell: A weapon obtained by defeating the Witness. Most powerful but slow compared to guns.<br>Shield: An item that can be obtained by defeating the Blind. Receives protection from enemies for a while.<br><br><strong><i>Map</i></strong><br>Space between reality and dream. You have to hold out until morning there. (99 seconds)<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1999910/extras/00f2946fc8f07b00d8088186e4a1da10.avif?t=1744102966\" width=300 height=150 /></span><br><strong><i>Survive nightmares for 99 seconds.</i></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1999910/extras/3a69b1dd72b42d7912fd4be5d8f28008.poster.avif?t=1744102966\" width=800 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1999910/extras/3a69b1dd72b42d7912fd4be5d8f28008.webm?t=1744102966\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1999910/extras/3a69b1dd72b42d7912fd4be5d8f28008.mp4?t=1744102966\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Coming soon.",
